  "description": "The image depicts a rocky coastal scene with tide pools and weathered rock formations. The foreground is dominated by large, dark-colored rocks covered in patches of green and reddish-brown algae or barnacles, surrounding small pools of still, greenish water. The rocks are eroded and have a rough texture. In the mid-ground, there are more rocks and further tide pools.  In the background, a larger, more distant rock formation is visible against a blue sky with scattered white clouds. The overall impression is one of a rugged, natural coastline environment.",
